Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:31.34,paper,,0,0,0,,{\pos(377,129)}第十
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:31.34,paper,,0,0,0,,{\pos(367,157)}大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:31.34,paper,,0,0,0,,{\pos(316,181)}雨過天晴心和暢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:31.34,paper,,0,0,0,,{\pos(319,302)}欲照山櫻日影長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:31.34,paper,,0,0,0,,{\pos(370,324)}運勢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太好了  小千
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.35,0:09:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,第十六籤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼啦  折木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.86,0:09:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,今年看來會有好事發生呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你是抽到末吉了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs20}末吉：一般而言，是除了凶以及大凶以外最不好的籤
